name: MutualAgreement
label: mutual agreement
definition: agreement between two or more specific named parties whereby the rights and obligations embodied in the agreement cannot be transferred to another party without prior agreement

name: Agreement
definition: negotiated understanding between two or more parties, reflecting the offer and acceptance of commitments on the part of either party
label: agreement
explanatoryNote: All agreements are time bound, whether implicit or explicitly stated, and thus an agreement reflects a state of affairs that holds for some period of time.

name: Obligor
label: obligor
definition: party that is bound legally or by agreement to repay a debt, make a payment, do something, or refrain from doing something

name: Obligee
definition: party to whom some commitment or obligation is owed, either legally or per the terms of an agreement
label: obligee

name: IndividualUnilateralCommitment
label: individual unilateral commitment
definition: commitment made by some party unilaterally to another specific party

name: UnilateralCommitment
definition: commitment made by one party without reference any other the party to which the commitment is made
label: unilateral commitment

name: MutualCommitment
definition: commitment between two or more parties
label: mutual commitment

name: Commitment
explanatoryNote: Such a promise often results a corresponding right or obligation with respect to another party to the commitment. Thus, obligations and rights are considered as reciprocal aspects of a commitment.
label: commitment
definition: promise made by some party to act or refrain from acting in some manner

name: Beneficiary
label: beneficiary
definition: party that receives some benefit or advantage or profits from something

name: CommitmentAtLarge
definition: commitment made by some party without direct involvement from the potential beneficiaries of that commitment
label: commitment at large

name: hasObligation
definition: identifies a duty or obligation that a given party has taken on
label: has obligation

name: isObligationOf
label: is obligation of
definition: identifies a party that has a given obligation
